"I thought perhaps something had hap- pened/' she said with her unchanging stonily severe expression; and, sitting down opposite the prince, she prepared to listen. 
"I wished to get a nap, mon cousin, but I can't." 
"Well, my dear?" said Prince Vasili, taking her hand and bending it downwards as was his habit. 
It was plain that this "well?" referred to much that they both understood without nam- ing.
